# Movie Review Sentiment Analysis using NLP

## Project Overview
This project uses Natural Language Processing (NLP) and Machine Learning techniques to classify IMDb movie reviews as Positive or Negative.

## Features
- Text preprocessing
- Stopword removal
- Stemming
- TF-IDF Vectorization
- Sentiment prediction
- Confusion matrix visualization

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NLTK
- Scikit-learn
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn

## Dataset
IMDb Movie Reviews Dataset

## Machine Learning Model
- Logistic Regression

## Workflow
1. Data Loading
2. Text Cleaning
3. Feature Extraction using TF-IDF
4. Model Training
5. Prediction
6. Evaluation

## Results
The model successfully predicts positive and negative movie reviews with good accuracy.

